public static java.lang.String getRandomizedBat(java.lang.String idBat,

Helper method for randomize attr, but tastes great all by itself if you know what you're doing. Given two (synchronized, as in coming from the same NST) BATs, one with OIDs and one with attr values, return a single BAT with OID head values and attr tail values.
